{"tid":1346951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"促請各界全力支持成立＂香港人民自衛隊＂","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T19:00:35.000Z","uid":244802,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf63895303be0dd841884525bfa656ca2bafac8","tid":1346951,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"由於現時香港已有部分地區長期持續處於無法治狀態，本應維持法治及執法者，即香港政府及香港警察因政治問題繼而引發一連串於香港發生之暴力及衝突事件，均未能即時及有效解決並保護香港市民人生安全，令香港市民時刻生命自由受到強烈威脅，大眾市民長時間處於不安以致恐慌狀態，若情況持續恐發生更大型災難，鑒於以上各種原因，本人謹此呼籲社會各界能自發成立＂香港人民自衛隊＂以保社會大眾安全。<br />\n<br />\n各位手足麻煩幫推,推到自衛隊成立,解放一班因為收入問題無法出黎幫手既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcf8f534c32c15aec5e45d31fc6555f20025c8e","tid":1346951,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f946ee835ebdde56661aca3742a6fc13dc3e704","tid":1346951,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"3bb9980302aa97cf1a375f0672f0e34a7f56ef57","tid":1346951,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162ceedb9a168b838036f0b27bb6b9bfd7a98df6","tid":1346951,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a62cfc7a7bbb5df81eda43ebf48461a8a7d6b9","tid":1346951,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k